[*]
[*] DFV Dual-LFSR Debug Waveform
[*] Observe how set/release mechanism creates synchronized stall release
[*] and whether same-cycle collisions occur at the cache bank.
[*]
[dumpfile] "run.vcd"
[timestart] 0
[size] 1920 1080
[pos] -1 -1
[treeopen] TOP.
[treeopen] TOP.rtlsim_shim.
[treeopen] TOP.rtlsim_shim.vortex.

