[*]
[*] HOW TO READ:
[*] 1. Find a dfv_release pulse (Group 1)
[*] 2. Check both stall_active signals drop in the SAME cycle
[*] 3. Measure latency from dcache gate slave_valid to bank core_req_valid (Group 7)
[*] 4. Measure latency from fill gate slave_valid to bank mem_rsp_valid (Group 7)
[*] 5. If latencies differ, events can't collide at the bank
[*]
